description: Filled with stunts and craziness, some of which contains mostly footage that the censors wouldn't allow on MTV. One stunt was once believed to end Steve-O's career, it was that insane.
name: Don't Try This at Home: The Steve-O Video

review.name: I enjoy steveo's Tapes more than CKY
review.reviewBody: I own both of Steveos Don't try this on VHS and it gives you a good look at what people found funny in the early early 2000s...they are great to still watch at Midnight, but a lot of homo situations mixed in with naked females
